comments[9]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T21:49:02.011Z",codex-agent,Created to track full-repo audit findings and warning-first hardening implementation.
  "2026-04-01T21:49:16.626Z",codex-agent,"Audit baseline (full repo): prioritized findings are silent settings fallback on invalid JSON, lock read/parse failures collapsing to stale behavior without diagnostics, unreadable item skips without visibility, and docs/package metadata drift (calendar versioning wording + repository links + packaged community docs). Chosen implementation policy is warn-continue to preserve compatibility while improving diagnosability."
  "2026-04-01T21:55:25.517Z",codex-agent,"Implemented runtime warning-first hardening slice 1: settings reads now emit deterministic warning tokens on invalid JSON/schema fallbacks; lock stale conflicts include deterministic warning tokens when lock metadata is unreadable/invalid; item-store listing paths now collect deterministic warning tokens for unreadable item files and non-ENOENT directory read failures."
  "2026-04-01T21:56:15.163Z",codex-agent,"Implemented docs/package metadata alignment: changelog header now references calendar versioning policy, package repository/homepage/bugs URLs now point to unbrained org, and npm files allowlist now includes CHANGELOG/CONTRIBUTING/SECURITY/CODE_OF_CONDUCT for packaged community guidance parity."
  "2026-04-01T21:57:47.380Z",codex-agent,"Targeted test hardening complete: added assertions for settings warning tokens, lock unreadable metadata warning token propagation, and item-store unreadable file warning emission. Verification: pnpm build passed; focused suite node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- [settings-store core-item-lock-coverage item-store config health list search calendar context] passed 9 files / 110 tests."
  "2026-04-01T22:01:22.465Z",codex-agent,"Verification evidence: pm test pm-4vm7 --run --timeout 7200 --json passed all linked commands (full regression suite, focused warning-hardening suite, and pnpm build). Additional coverage run node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed with thresholds met (All files: statements 94.4, branches 91.49, functions 96.12, lines 94.7)."
  "2026-04-12T15:37:21.444Z",codex-agent,"Execution kickoff (2026-04-12): duplicate-check evidence rerun with pm context --limit 10; pm search 'full-repo issue sweep remediation' --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20; pm list-blocked --limit 20. Reusing and reopening pm-4vm7 as canonical scope for full-repo errors+warnings sweep to avoid duplicate task creation."
  "2026-04-12T15:48:58.194Z",codex-agent,"Fix pass: addressed Vitest warnings about non-top-level hoisted unmock calls by replacing vi.unmock with vi.doUnmock in cleanup paths for tests/unit/vector-store-adapter.spec.ts and tests/unit/item-format-toon-decode-error.spec.ts. Targeted verification passed with no warning emissions: pnpm exec vitest run tests/unit/vector-store-adapter.spec.ts tests/unit/item-format-toon-decode-error.spec.ts."
  "2026-04-12T16:00:43.955Z",codex-agent,"Final verification rerun (post-fix) passed cleanly with no Vitest warning emissions: pm --version; node -v; pnpm -v; pnpm version:check; pnpm security:scan; pnpm build; pnpm typecheck; pnpm test (75 files / 1020 tests); pnpm test:coverage (75 files / 1020 tests, coverage 100/100/100/100); node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (75 files / 1020 tests, coverage 100/100/100/100); npm pack --dry-run; pnpm smoke:npx."
